This project includes protocol structure and behaviour derived from
study of the "necromancer" project (Apache-2.0):

  https://github.com/micolous/necromancer

Attribution: Michael Farrell and necromancer contributors.

UDP trait signatures in this crate follow the `edge-nal` 0.6 `UdpSend` / `UdpReceive`
contracts (MIT OR Apache-2.0) without linking that crate, so host `cargo test` stays
free of `embassy-time` driver symbols.
